summary: listen, if nintendo ever decides to make a mario movie following pokemon and sonic, the only movie i will accept is a...
body:
listen, if nintendo ever decides to make a mario movie following pokemon and sonic, the only movie i will accept is a maleficent-esque film where we learn the true backstory of bowser — that he’s this big bad revolution leader fighting for gay rights in the mushroom kingdom, and princess peach is also trying to convince the king (her dad) to say ‘hell yeah gay rights’ since her best friend, daisy, is a lesbian, but the king is super stubborn/homophobic so peach has a clandestine meeting with bowser where she proposes they stage a kidnapping in which bowser promises to return peach if the king finally supports marriage equality, but the king is just that awful that he tasks mario with hunting down bowser and rescuing peach (not telling him that there’s a simpler solution)

i don’t have all the details worked out but bowser would marry his longtime boyfriend petey piranha, bowser jr. would be mischievously supportive of his two dads, kamek would be a drag queen, trans icon birdo would throw the first egg at stonewall, and it would obviously be called “So Long, Gay Bowser”
